.TH TRANSCRIBE 1 "April 2026" "dictee 1.3.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
transcribe \- transcribe audio files using NVIDIA Parakeet TDT
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B transcribe
.I audio_file
.RI [ model_dir ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B transcribe
converts speech in audio files to text using the NVIDIA Parakeet TDT model.
Supports 25 languages with automatic language detection. Includes native
punctuation and capitalization.
.PP
Accepts any audio format (MP3, OGG, FLAC, OPUS, etc.) via automatic
.BR ffmpeg (1)
conversion to WAV 16kHz mono.
File paths support
.BR ~ ", " ./ ", and " ../
resolution.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.I audio_file
Path to the audio file to transcribe (required). Any format supported
by ffmpeg is accepted.
.TP
.I model_dir
Path to TDT model directory (default: /usr/share/dictee/tdt).
.TP
.BR \-\-help ", " \-h
Display a brief usage summary and exit.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Transcribe a WAV file:
.B transcribe recording.wav
.TP
Transcribe an MP3 file:
.B transcribe interview.mp3
.TP
Use custom model path:
.B transcribe recording.wav /path/to/tdt
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR transcribe\-daemon (1),
.BR transcribe\-client (1),
.BR transcribe\-diarize (1),
.BR dictee (1),
.BR ffmpeg (1)
